{"tid":1028150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烤鴨餅皮疑發霉　食客當葱花誤食：惡心兼反胃","createTime":"2019-02-19T09:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T10:41:34.000Z","uid":225464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e487c1b2cb7bed99f0524b82f300222ea8bb3f68","tid":1028150,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>烤鴨餅皮疑發霉 食客當葱花誤食：惡心兼反胃</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GOiX5P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GOiX5P&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=ba97933f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GOiX5P</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/photo/bkn-20190219163657048-0219_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190219170746\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190219%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190219163657048-0219_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190219170746&h=bba25713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n餅皮疑滿布霉菌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餅皮發霉，餐廳照奉客？近日有人於元朗光顧一間連鎖川菜餐廳時，發現烤鴨的餅皮疑滿布霉菌，直呼惡心。<br />\n<br />\n有食客在Facebook群組「巴打絲打Facebook Club」上載照片，表示於上周六（16日）晚上在元朗Yoho Mall一間川菜餐廳點了一客脆皮黃金烤鴨，餐廳同時奉上一份餅皮。起初他們誤以為表面的綠色點為葱花，誰知吃到第四塊時，始驚覺餅皮「發霉到一個極點」。<br />\n<br />\n他表示當時餐廳職員「笑笑口就拎走咗碟嘢，同我哋講話換過一份，但我哋都唔敢再食。」事後餐廳經理亦免卻飯錢作賠償，「但成個過程非常之惡心同反胃，返到屋企個肚成晚唔舒服，個心諗起呢一幕就反胃」。<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，不少網民同指惡心︰「呢個真係誇張」、「見到都反胃，間嘢想種菌」、「廚房咁都照出，勁」。<br />\n<br />\n《港呢啲》向有關餐廳了解事件，正候回覆。"},{"pid":"2aad18037b02402435b8783f62f29bf5a7d4b0ee","tid":1028150,"uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/photo/bkn-20190219163657048-0219_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190219170746\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190219%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190219163657048-0219_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190219170746&h=e3bcfe3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食客一度誤以為餅皮上是葱花。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"2efc24bbcd13a2b87c98a03a0fb7345f341531e0","tid":1028150,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">又係垃圾川菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"61bce432f6f52fe19073465822e9841a874b3270","tid":1028150,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"哇屌<br />\n好撚想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce57ba4639f893a9e49b7c6b658445272eb3785d","tid":1028150,"uid":1067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"驗吓眼同腦穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c88034e4d4e4851c2b4d1010adbb185818d78b","tid":1028150,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:09:07.000Z","msg":"蔥花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8b9334c39aaa5921e04362969cf3adbcca08b5","tid":1028150,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be7c0e28a51a346006ea106a0f77608817ac44e5","tid":1028150,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"牛肉加蔥花要烏冬嗎"},{"pid":"ab96ceb3237ceefe00ddee7c9aebe8469f073d46","tid":1028150,"uid":73,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"同張紙有d 似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8e75e36ef2910f60ee3b98a998b2dacb39e796","tid":1028150,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"邊撚度係䓤花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}